{"tid":1898491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府預留 4.5 億元 供律政司推行計劃「加深社會對法治認識及實踐」","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T06:49:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d0aa7f12b071bcba2e9a8d568b8af7ab34850627","tid":1898491,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波今日（26 日）到立法會宣讀新一份《財政預算案》。陳茂波宣讀報告「專業服務」章節時，提到尊重法治、司法獨立，是香港賴以成功的基石之一。他計劃預留約 4億 5 千萬元，讓律政司推行「願景 2030 &mdash; 聚焦法治」計劃，加深香港社會對法治概念的認識及實踐。"},{"pid":"c30e4c3976e6c040d4e00d51d32a0086b2c127da","tid":1898491,"uid":192935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"f4d106e9c42fa6889a4513a9832f145ab0bf00ab","tid":1898491,"uid":67454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:09:17.000Z","msg":"最唔明既係你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d67c811dbbfae3111cb82fdc8b6f0ad7667edb4","tid":1898491,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"又益咗連登女神奶媽驊"},{"pid":"7aeb37ffff0b8818aca5caa95355516fbf0d16c8","tid":1898491,"uid":214192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:26:13.000Z","msg":"明明政府就係最唔識法治嘅人<br />\n不如區議會拎錢宣傳法治啦，搵張達明呢啲大律師嚟講解咩叫法治 法治嘅層次 好過比港共拎嚟自己套概念"},{"pid":"83b9dbe61d44c8f68f2b11f7835a90ac42c0d4a4","tid":1898491,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"開支- 活動顧問費用咗4.45億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176d5f1e3ce6b766b2c8da47608bb6a3540431e2","tid":1898491